Unemployment is at a 50-year low.

Good news: 

Our economy added 250,000 jobs last month. That's on top of the 12 million jobs we've added since we came into office. The unemployment rate is at the lowest in 50 years, and working-age Americans are participating in the labor force at the highest rate in 15 years. https://t.co/PpdoqQSYnL

The American economy remains strong as it transitions to steady and stable growth.

Our economy added over 300,000 jobs a month during the quarter, the unemployment rate remained near a 50-year low, and workforce participation for working-age Americans is the highest in 15 years.
